title: Carb Smart Turkey and Spinach Meatballs with Red Pepper Pesto, Roasted Veggies and Garlic Toast
description: Tender meatballs float in red pepper pesto with blistered tomatoes and zucchini. Make sure to sop up the sauce with buttery garlic toast.

